    Building Microservices in springboot
In the past, what gets deployed is one entity and it scales as a single entity.
On the code side, you can have multiple modularity or projects but still have a monolith deployed.
But with micro services, what gets deployed is very different
    Todo
-Creating a few microservices.
-Having them communicate with each other.
-Monolith broken to micro services
-Difference between web service and micro service
    What is a Technology
A technology is used to solve a problem.
Technology we will use - Spring Cloud
Spring Cloud: This is one of the robust ways to create micro services.
